| Dimension | Status | Trend |
|----------|--------|-------|
| Deliveries | On Track / At Risk / Off Track | up / down / stable |
| Quality | On Track / At Risk / Off Track | up / down / stable |
| Metrics | On Track / At Risk / Off Track | up / down / stable |

