```

---

## Audience Variations

### For Squad (Detailed)
- Include technical details
- Engineering metrics (velocity, bugs)
- Specific tasks

### For Stakeholders (Executive)
- Focus on business metrics
- Highlight OKR impact
- Fewer technical details

### For Leadership (Ultra-concise)
- Only TL;DR + Overall Health + Blockers
- Maximum 1 page
- Focus on decisions needed

---

## Writing Guidelines

- **Factual:** Numbers over opinions
- **Actionable:** Each item should have owner and next step
- **Honest:** Don't hide problems, present with action plan
- **Concise:** Stakeholders have limited time

---

## Quality Checklist

Before sending, verify:

- [ ] TL;DR captures the 3 most important points
- [ ] Health status is realistic (not all green)
- [ ] Blockers have action and owner defined
- [ ] Metrics are up to date
- [ ] Next steps are specific and have dates
- [ ] Help needed is clear and actionable
